{"text_id":155305,"tokens":["The"," question"," of"," whether"," students"," should"," be"," required"," to"," complete"," summer"," assignments"," is"," a"," contentious"," one",","," with"," valid"," arguments"," on"," both"," sides","."," On"," one"," hand",","," summer"," assignments"," can"," help"," students"," retain"," the"," knowledge"," and"," skills"," they"," have"," acquired"," during"," the"," school"," year",","," and"," can"," prepare"," them"," for"," the"," upcoming"," academic"," term","."," On"," the"," other"," hand",","," summer"," assignments"," can"," be"," a"," source"," of"," stress"," and"," frustration"," for"," students",","," and"," may"," not"," be"," effective"," in"," promoting"," learning"," and"," retention",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," main"," arguments"," in"," favor"," of"," summer"," assignments"," is"," that"," they"," can"," help"," students"," retain"," the"," material"," they"," have"," learned"," during"," the"," school"," year","."," Research"," has"," shown"," that"," students"," can"," lose"," up"," to"," ","3","0","%"," of"," their"," academic"," skills"," over"," the"," summer"," months",","," a"," phenomenon"," known"," as"," the"," \"","summer"," slide",".\""," By"," requiring"," students"," to"," complete"," summer"," assignments",","," educators"," can"," help"," combat"," this"," loss"," of"," knowledge"," and"," skills",","," and"," ensure"," that"," students"," are"," ready"," to"," hit"," the"," ground"," running"," when"," the"," new"," school"," year"," begins",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," summer"," assignments"," can"," provide"," students"," with"," the"," opportunity"," to"," explore"," topics"," of"," personal"," interest"," in"," greater"," depth","."," For"," example",","," a"," student"," who"," is"," interested"," in"," history"," might"," be"," required"," to"," read"," a"," book"," or"," complete"," a"," research"," project"," on"," a"," particular"," historical"," event"," or"," figure","."," This"," type"," of"," assignment"," can"," not"," only"," help"," students"," retain"," their"," knowledge"," and"," skills",","," but"," can"," also"," foster"," a"," love"," of"," learning"," and"," a"," deeper"," understanding"," of"," the"," subject"," matter",".","\n\n","However",","," there"," are"," also"," several"," potential"," drawbacks"," to"," summer"," assignments","."," One"," of"," the"," main"," concerns"," is"," that"," summer"," assignments"," can"," be"," a"," source"," of"," stress"," and"," frustration"," for"," students","."," Many"," students"," already"," have"," busy"," schedules"," during"," the"," summer"," months",","," with"," activities"," such"," as"," sports",","," camps",","," and"," vacations","."," Adding"," summer"," assignments"," to"," the"," mix"," can"," be"," overwhelming",","," and"," can"," take"," away"," from"," the"," enjoyment"," and"," relaxation"," that"," students"," should"," be"," experiencing"," during"," their"," time"," off"," from"," school",".","\n\n","Another"," concern"," is"," that"," summer"," assignments"," may"," not"," be"," effective"," in"," promoting"," learning"," and"," retention","."," Research"," has"," shown"," that"," students"," often"," do"," not"," complete"," summer"," assignments",","," or"," do"," not"," complete"," them"," thoroughly","."," This"," can"," be"," due"," to"," a"," lack"," of"," motivation",","," a"," lack"," of"," time",","," or"," a"," lack"," of"," resources","."," As"," a"," result",","," summer"," assignments"," may"," not"," have"," the"," desired"," effect"," of"," helping"," students"," retain"," their"," knowledge"," and"," skills",".","\n\n","Additionally",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," consider"," the"," differing"," student"," conditions"," when"," it"," comes"," to"," summer"," assignments","."," Not"," all"," students"," have"," the"," same"," access"," to"," resources",","," such"," as"," books"," and"," technology",","," which"," can"," make"," it"," difficult"," for"," them"," to"," complete"," summer"," assignments","."," Furthermore",","," some"," students"," may"," not"," have"," a"," conducive"," learning"," environment"," at"," home",","," which"," can"," make"," it"," challenging"," for"," them"," to"," focus"," and"," complete"," their"," work",".","\n\n","In"," my"," personal"," experience",","," I"," have"," seen"," both"," the"," benefits"," and"," drawbacks"," of"," summer"," assignments","."," As"," a"," student",","," I"," found"," that"," summer"," assignments"," could"," be"," a"," helpful"," way"," to"," review"," material"," and"," prepare"," for"," the"," upcoming"," school"," year","."," However",","," I"," also"," found"," that"," summer"," assignments"," could"," be"," a"," source"," of"," stress"," and"," frustration",","," particularly"," if"," they"," were"," long"," or"," complex",".","\n\n","As"," a"," teacher",","," I"," have"," seen"," the"," benefits"," of"," summer"," assignments"," in"," terms"," of"," student"," retention"," and"," preparedness","."," However",","," I"," have"," also"," seen"," the"," challenges"," that"," students"," face"," in"," completing"," summer"," assignments",","," particularly"," if"," they"," do"," not"," have"," access"," to"," the"," necessary"," resources"," or"," a"," conducive"," learning"," environment",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," question"," of"," whether"," students"," should"," be"," required"," to"," complete"," summer"," assignments"," is"," a"," complex"," one",","," with"," valid"," arguments"," on"," both"," sides","."," Summer"," assignments"," can"," be"," a"," helpful"," way"," to"," promote"," learning"," and"," retention",","," but"," they"," can"," also"," be"," a"," source"," of"," stress"," and"," frustration"," for"," students","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," consider"," the"," individual"," needs"," and"," circumstances"," of"," students"," when"," it"," comes"," to"," summer"," assignments",","," and"," to"," ensure"," that"," they"," have"," the"," necessary"," resources"," and"," support"," to"," complete"," their"," work","."," Ultimately",","," the"," decision"," of"," whether"," or"," not"," to"," require"," summer"," assignments"," should"," be"," based"," on"," the"," needs"," and"," goals"," of"," the"," students"," and"," the"," school",","," and"," should"," be"," made"," with"," careful"," consideration"," of"," the"," potential"," benefits"," and"," drawbacks","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}